                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>« <a href="/news-03-2016">March 2016</a> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;">April 2016</span> | <a href="/news-05-2016">May 2016</a> »</strong></p>
</div>
<p>No, you're two weeks late! Welcome to this installment of site news, the only news outlet that cares enough to listen to you drunkenly ramble at 3AM! This is a series showing off news from the site, articles from the past month, and fan-content for you to check out and discover! Be sure to leave a comment with your thoughts!</p>
<h3 id="toc0"><span>On-Site News</span></h3>
<h4 id="toc1"><span>Featured Articles</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>The featured articles for this month are <a href="/scp-2985">SCP-2985</a> (&quot;Anart, Author of the Scream&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>, and <a href="/exploration-log-2474-1">Exploration Log 2474-1</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>! One's about the struggle to maintain artistic integrity in a world that wants you to fail, and the other is about a task force daring to explore a desolate planet. Check them out!</li>
<li>The featured articles from last month were <a href="/scp-1340">SCP-1340</a> (&quot;The Fraternal Order of the Cave Mantas&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;">LurkD</a></span>, <a href="/scp-245">SCP-245</a> (&quot;SCP-RPG&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;">Doctor Cimmerian</a></span>, <a href="/scp-2875">SCP-2875</a> (&quot;The Town That Got Fucked By Bears&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, and <a href="/i-hope-that-i-get-old-before-i-die">I Hope That I Get Old Before I Die</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">Roget</a></span>. One's about a conglomerate of talking sea animals, the second's about an entity that needs someone to play it, the third is about <em>a goddamn bear-arena</em>, and the fourth is about coming to terms with a relative slowly fading. Check them out if you missed it!</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc2"><span>Rest of the News</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>March Madness has concluded! It was a long, hard tournament. But eventually <a href="/scp-777-j">SCP-777-J</a>, <a href="/scp-2776">SCP-2776</a> and <a href="/scp-1569">SCP-1569</a> stood victorious amongst the rabble. Give them a hand! Also give a hand to the real winners, Hercules Rockefeller, and Jacob Conwell!</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>As always, here's everything that was posted during the month of April, with the best* pithy summaries money can buy.</p>
<h3 id="toc3"><span>Week of April 1st</span></h3>
<p>The week of April 1st began tragically when #site19 was involved in a horrible kicking spree. Pray for all who were lost.</p>
<h4 id="toc4"><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2435">SCP-2435</a> (&quot;Empty Space&quot;) - Don’t touch the box. Nothing will happen, and it’ll hurt like hell. Researched by <span class="error-inline"><em>TheSapientOne</em> does not match any existing user name</span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2862">SCP-2862</a> (&quot;Beholder&quot;) - This is how Alfred Hitchcock movies start. Cataloged by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4275444); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4275444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="faminepulse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4275444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4275444); return false;">faminepulse</a></span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2806">SCP-2806</a> (&quot;We Have the Technology&quot;) - Gentlemen, we can rebuild him. We have the technology… in a limited stage of pre-development. Product testing by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2645">SCP-2645</a> (&quot;Through the Looking Glass&quot;) - Sometime the looking glass doesn’t want you to come through. <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ribby97" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2299134); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2299134&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="ribby97" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2299134)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ribby97" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2299134); return false;">ribby97</a></span> gazed long into the abyss.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2308">SCP-2308</a> (&quot;Futures Trading&quot;) - As it turns out, time travel isn't a safe investment strategy after all. Prime financial advice by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc5"><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/unsaved-world">Unsaved World</a> - Is that what you think? That this is necessary? That this is just? Does your arrogance have no end? Written and translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blackbird5154" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2074508); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2074508&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Blackbird5154" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2074508)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blackbird5154" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2074508); return false;">Blackbird5154</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/the-maker-and-the-beast">The Maker and the Beast</a> -</li>
</ul>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><tt>Volume 03.17-L-02&#160;1. The Mother and Maker gazed upon the world.<br />
2. They knew only one could prosper.<br />
3. And the owner would be decided by steel.</tt><br />
- Transcribed by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span></p>
</div>
<ul>
<li><a href="/home-is-a-place-with-mushrooms">Home is a Place With Mushrooms</a> - Quick tip - you can cut your containment breach time by 50% if you use a glitch in the elevators to clip through the wall and skip to the bottom level instantly. Run time record set by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;">Agent MacLeod</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/party-of-gods">Not a contest entry, but a crackfic about gods anyways</a> - The gods gathered at the Great Abyss like flies attracted to rotten meat, hunting each other down and licking the wounds of the universe. They were also throwing a party, overseen by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc6"><span>GoI Formats</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/spc-140">SPC-140</a> - The tale of the Sharkic war is a long and bloody one. It’s up to us to make it longer and bloodier. Pugilistic warfare developed by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;">sirpudding</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/grant-request-for-genetically-engineering-low-cost-organic-a">GRANT REQUEST FOR GENETICALLY ENGINEERING LOW-COST ORGANIC AUTOMATONS WITH SOPHISTICATED ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE FOR LABOR</a> - There’s no way this could go wrong, right guys? Right? Abominations unto God created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc7"><span>Misc</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/extended-scp-420-j-experiment-log">Extended SCP-420-J Experiment Log</a> - Yo man, I have had some really, really nice ████ in my day, but this definitely takes the cake. Huh? Where’d I get it? Talk to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quikngruvn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(333389); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=333389&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Quikngruvn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=333389)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quikngruvn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(333389); return false;">Quikngruvn</a></span>, man.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc8"><span>Week of April 8th</span></h3>
<p>Apparently they're giving out free drinks at the Site 23 break room. You better hurry, Bright's starting to make a mess of things.</p>
<h4 id="toc9"><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-724-j">SCP-724-J</a> (&quot;Bad Roach&quot;) - WANTED FOR THEFT, ASSAULT, DRIVING UNDER THE INFLUENCE, ARSON, AND WANTON DISREGARD OF TOBACCO ADVOCACY NOTICES. IF SEEN REPORT TO <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2034230&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="daveyoufool" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2034230)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;">daveyoufool</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2696">SCP-2696</a> (&quot;The Haunted Victorian Mansion of Dark Peak&quot;) - A father does what he must to preserve all that’s left of his family. Recounted by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2457">SCP-2457</a> (&quot;母を見たい&quot;) - Being unable to conceive a child can be a distressing thought. Some people come up with more creative solutions than others. Medical exam performed by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;">MrWrong</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2243">SCP-2243</a> (&quot;Peep Peepers&quot;) - If a finch could speak, we could not understand him. But <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nibarlan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2678022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2678022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Nibarlan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2678022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nibarlan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2678022); return false;">Nibarlan</a></span> gives it a shot.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2934">SCP-2934</a> (&quot;The Tower and the Pit&quot;) - <tt>production will continue until the final product has been developed. production must not be halted. do not fear the results of production. granted at request of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span></tt>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2241">SCP-2241</a> (&quot;Cameron The Crusader&quot;) - What room for heroes is there in worlds such as these? <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(462110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=462110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="Tuomey Tombstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=462110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(462110); return false;">Tuomey Tombstone</a></span> tries to answer.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2910">SCP-2910</a> (&quot;That Only a Mother&quot;) - Congratulations to the possible mother of a healthy affront to God! Delivered by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152676" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc10"><span>Tales</span></h4>
