<li><a href="/to-settle-all-accounts-of-the-butt">To Settle All Accounts of the Butt</a> - We don't all get parodies. But at the very least, we need to say raspberry noises. Lampooned by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152677" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;">Randomini</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/the-last-good-man-in-the-foundation">The Last Good Man in the Foundation</a> - Whoever judges what's for the greater good, they're clearly wrong; otherwise we wouldn't be in this mess. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152677" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/what-s-real">What's Real?</a> - It's not a werewolf. It's a hybrid of Homo sapiens and Canis lupus that happens to be allergic to the atomic structure of silver. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ian-is-me" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315643); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1315643&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152677" alt="Ian is Me" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1315643)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ian-is-me" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315643); return false;">Ian is Me</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/the-harold-maine-fan-club">The Harold Maine Fan Club</a>; <a href="/autocorrect">Autocorrect</a>; <a href="/paris-texas">Paris, Texas</a>; <a href="/7-degrees-of-separation">7 Degrees of Separation</a>; <a href="/webs">Webs</a> - Entries two through six in <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wils" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2096532); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2096532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596152677" alt="Wils" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2096532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wils" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2096532); return false;">Wils</a></span> ongoing series about a bad guy who has a phone that does bad things, and his victims, who have to do what he says else risk being turned into God knows what.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc20"><span>Fandom Stuff</span></h3>
<p>What's been going on in the community aside from our site? Well&#8230;</p>
<ul>
<li>In Glasgow, the <a href="https://www.rcs.ac.uk/plug-is-10-years-old/">Royal Conservatoire of Scotland</a> performed a concert partially inspired by the music of the SCP Foundation</li>
<li><a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/375580/">Three Days</a>, an SCP fangame by <a href="https://twitter.com/GorePixelGames">GorePixelGames</a>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc21"><span>Fanart</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>Peep this awesome drawing of 076 by Tumblr user <a href="http://kaoru222.tumblr.com/post/142405111384/%E3%81%93%E3%81%AE%E7%B5%B5%E3%81%AF%E5%8E%9F%E8%91%97%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E3%81%AEscp-076%E3%81%AB%E5%9F%BA%E3%81%A5%E3%81%8D%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99httpwwwscp-wikinets">Kaoru222</a>.</li>
<li>In which <a href="http://chicken0215.tumblr.com/post/142333939150/scp-999profsnider">Chicken0215</a> actually makes 999 cute enough for me to like.</li>
<li><a href="http://surumerume.tumblr.com/post/142063145715/april-1-is-a-day-of-the-liars-i-drew-it-%E9%8A%83%E9%A0%91%E5%BC%B5%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E9%8A%83%E5%A5%BD%E3%81%8D">Surumerume</a> presents: The Day of Liars!</li>
<li><a href="http://kibadori-rue.tumblr.com/post/142515306259/scp-666-j">Kibadori</a> makes 666-J way more fucking badass than I ever imagined it could be. They also drew this awesome drawing of <a href="https://kibadori-rue.tumblr.com/post/143840669319/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A8%E3%81%A1%E3%82%83%E3%83%BC%E3%82%93-scp-811-pigcatapult">SCP-811 by Pig Catapult!</a></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>That's a wrap for this month folks! Again, apologies for the lateness, and expect to see Decibelle back in her normal position next month. I hope you all have a great month, and wish you the best of luck with your endeavors.</p>
